      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-200 Cyclone&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-2 body, which is a multi-purpose hybrid missile designed to penetrate point defense grids.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_BLASTFRAG warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using a Passive Wake seeker.

